location is Diamond Hill State Park in Cumberland; take I-295 to
Exit 11(?) then north on Route 114

gates open at 8am, $10 for show cars, $15 for vendors of used
parts, $15 for vendors of new parts, drive up in a VW and admission
is free whether you're showing or not

